1830:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****   *        in order to provide the accurate value :
1831:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_uart.c ****   *        In Interrupt Mode :
